BT 0 g /F2 15 Tf 212.4 750 Td (WHAT IS ANGER? \(Real Talk\)) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 740 m 562 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 715 Td (Let's be honest: everyone gets angry. Your parents, your teachers,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 698 Td (your friends - literally everyone. Anger is a NORMAL emotion. It's not) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 681 Td (bad or wrong to feel angry. The problem only starts when anger makes) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 664 Td (you do things you regret.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 647 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 630 Td (WHY DO TEENS GET SO ANGRY?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 613 Td (- Your brain is literally under construction \(prefrontal cortex developing\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 596 Td (- Hormones are all over the place) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 579 Td (- You're dealing with more social pressure than ever) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 562 Td (- You want independence but still have rules to follow) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 545 Td (- School stress, friend drama, family issues - it's a LOT) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 528 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 511 Td (ANGER IS A SECONDARY EMOTION) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 494 Td (Under anger, there's usually something else:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 477 Td (  - Feeling disrespected or embarrassed) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 460 Td (  - Feeling hurt or rejected) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 443 Td (  - Feeling scared or anxious) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 426 Td (  - Feeling powerless or unheard) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 409 Td (  - Feeling overwhelmed) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 392 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 375 Td (THIS WORKBOOK WILL HELP YOU:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 358 Td (- Understand YOUR anger \(everyone's is different\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 341 Td (- Catch it before it explodes) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 324 Td (- Handle it without making things worse) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 307 Td (- Communicate what you actually need) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 290 Td (- Stop the guilt/shame cycle after blowups) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 273 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 256 Td (You're not broken. You just need better tools.) Tj ET

endstream
