BT 0 g /F2 15 Tf 244.8 750 Td (THE VOLCANO MODEL) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 217.2 732 Td (Anger has levels - know where you are) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 722 m 562 722 l S Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 695 Td (LEVEL 5 - ERUPTION \(10/10\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 60 679 Td (Full explosion. Yelling, breaking things, saying horrible things.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 60 665 Td (You can't think. Adrenaline has taken over completely.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 60 651 Td (RECOVERY TIME: 30-60 minutes minimum) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 625 Td (LEVEL 4 - ABOUT TO BLOW \(7-9/10\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 60 609 Td (Shouting, aggressive body language, threatening.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 60 595 Td (Still a tiny bit of control. THIS IS YOUR LAST CHANCE to use tools.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 60 581 Td (BEST MOVE: Walk away NOW. No discussion. Just leave safely.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 555 Td (LEVEL 3 - HEATING UP \(5-6/10\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 60 539 Td (Arguing, raised voice, sarcasm, door slamming.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 60 525 Td (You can still think but it's getting harder.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 60 511 Td (BEST MOVE: Use a cool-down strategy. Tell them you need a minute.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 485 Td (LEVEL 2 - WARMING \(3-4/10\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 60 469 Td (Irritated, annoyed, eye-rolling, short responses.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 60 455 Td (You can still make good choices easily here.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 60 441 Td (BEST MOVE: Name it. 'I'm getting frustrated.' Use a strategy.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 415 Td (LEVEL 1 - CALM \(1-2/10\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 60 399 Td (Chill, relaxed, can handle things that come up.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 60 385 Td (This is where you build skills and make plans.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 60 371 Td (BEST MOVE: Practice your strategies so they're automatic.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 340 Td (Right now I'm usually at Level ___ when I start my strategies.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 324 Td (I want to start catching myself at Level ___.) Tj ET

endstream
