BT 0 g /F2 15 Tf 216.0 750 Td (COOL-DOWN STRATEGIES MENU) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 200.4 732 Td (Pick 5 favorites and practice them when calm) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 722 m 562 722 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 700 Td (1. Box breathing \(4 in, 4 hold, 4 out, 4 hold\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 683 Td (2. Squeeze an ice cube in your hand \(pain redirect\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 666 Td (3. Sprint or do jumping jacks for 60 seconds) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 649 Td (4. Listen to ONE song \(loud, with headphones\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 632 Td (5. Count backwards from 100 by 7s) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 615 Td (6. Cold water on wrists and face) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 598 Td (7. Text a friend about something totally different) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 581 Td (8. Draw your anger \(abstract scribbles count\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 564 Td (9. Write down everything you want to say \(don't send\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 547 Td (10. Do 20 push-ups or wall sits) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 530 Td (11. Name 5 things you can see, 4 hear, 3 touch, 2 smell, 1 taste) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 513 Td (12. Rip up paper into tiny pieces) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 496 Td (13. Put in earbuds and listen to a guided meditation \(even 2 min\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 479 Td (14. Go outside - just stand outside for 2 minutes) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 462 Td (15. Squeeze a stress ball until your hand is tired) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 445 Td (16. Watch a funny video \(have one saved for emergencies\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 428 Td (17. Chew gum aggressively) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 411 Td (18. Take a shower \(water resets your nervous system\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 394 Td (19. Journal stream-of-consciousness for 5 minutes) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 377 Td (20. Play a simple phone game \(Tetris, puzzle\) for 5 min) Tj ET
