BT 0 g /F2 15 Tf 223.2 750 Td (ASSERTIVE vs AGGRESSIVE) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 740 m 562 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 715 Td (AGGRESSIVE = Getting your way by intimidation, yelling, threatening) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 699 Td (  Result: People fear you, avoid you, don't trust you) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 683 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 667 Td (PASSIVE = Saying nothing, bottling it up, people-pleasing) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 651 Td (  Result: Resentment builds, eventually explodes 10x worse) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 635 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 619 Td (ASSERTIVE = Saying what you need clearly, calmly, respectfully) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 603 Td (  Result: People respect you, problems get solved, you feel empowered) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 587 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 571 Td (THE ASSERTIVE FORMULA FOR TEENS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 555 Td (  'I feel [emotion] when [specific thing happens]) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 539 Td (   because [why it matters to me].) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 523 Td (   What I need is [specific request].') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 507 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 491 Td (EXAMPLES:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 475 Td (Instead of: 'GET OUT OF MY ROOM OR I'LL BREAK YOUR STUFF!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 459 Td (Try: 'I feel frustrated when you come in without knocking because) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 443 Td (I need privacy. Can you please knock first?') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 427 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 411 Td (Instead of: 'You're the WORST teacher. This class is stupid.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 395 Td (Try: 'I'm confused about this assignment. Can I get help) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 379 Td (understanding what you expect?') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 363 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 347 Td (Instead of: \(saying nothing and ghosting a friend who hurt you\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 331 Td (Try: 'I felt hurt when you said that in front of everyone.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 315 Td (Our friendship matters to me. Can we talk about it?') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 299 Td () Tj ET
