q 0 G 1 w 50 722 m 562 722 l S Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 695 Td (A REAL apology has 5 parts:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 673 Td (1. NAME what you did \(no minimizing\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 657 Td (   'I [specific thing I did]...') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 641 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 625 Td (2. ACKNOWLEDGE how it affected them) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 609 Td (   'I know that made you feel [emotion]...') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 593 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 577 Td (3. TAKE RESPONSIBILITY \(no 'but'\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 561 Td (   'That was wrong of me. There's no excuse.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 545 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 529 Td (4. SAY WHAT YOU'LL DO DIFFERENTLY) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 513 Td (   'Next time, I will [specific different action]...') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 497 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 481 Td (5. ASK if there's anything else they need) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 465 Td (   'Is there anything else I can do to make this right?') Tj ET
